business_name: 干洗裁缝店 Rockdale Drycleaner
details_html:
如果您的衣柜里总有一些完好却过时的衣服，你也许永远都不再穿，但扔了又可惜，怎么办呢？找我呀！你的衣服我做主，稍微调整一下创意，您就会拥有独一无二的款式！相信我的创意!

干洗，熨烫，裁缝，修改，成衣制作，成衣修改，西服设计和定制。婚纱，礼服设计，定制，修改或出租。

另有洗包包，洗鞋子，洗棉被，洗毛毯等服务，欢迎光临。

地址：9A King St, Rockdale, NSW 2216 电话：02 9567 2890 / 0449 850 688 微信：Eucalyptus123

WSF clothing shop can help relieve stress from your busy week by taking care of your laundry & dry cleaning needs delivering your washing to you at affordable prices.

Through our quality laundry & dry cleaning services your washing can be collected, wash, dry cleaned, ironed and delivered to your doorstep to suit your schedule saving you time and money.

We welcome all local sports teams who need their kits washing on a weekly basis and can offer an exceptional service at a very competitive price, so you and your team mates have a cleaner then clean kit every week.

Our dry cleaning includes:

Two day turnarounds
Express same day service
Free collection & delivery
Shirt service
Curtains & bed linen dry cleaning
Corporate/office dry cleaning
Suit & wedding dress specialists
Very competitive rates

Our laundry & alterations include:

Laundry services
Ironing services
Tailor alterations
Clothing repairs
